## Pages

all the pages: main nav, footer

* `/` - home page with some intro text
* `/houses` - menu with all the trails (link to `/trails/:id`) plus a "all" item (link to `/houses`), list of all the houses
* `/houses/:id` - details of the house and a link to its trailer
* `/trails` - redirect to /houses
* `/trails/:id` - list of all the houses of the selected trail
* `/artists` - menu with all the artforms (link to `/artforms/:id`) plus a "all" item (link to `/artists`), list of all the artists
* `/artists/:id` - details of the artist and a link to its house
* `/artforms` - redirect to /artists
* `/artforms/:id` - list of all the artists of the selected artform
* `/404` - error page
* `/*` - redirect to 404 page


## Components

* main nav: home - trails - artists
* list (with links) of the houses with the applied filter
* list (with links) of the artists with the applied filter
* cat nav: trails
* cat nav: artforms
* detail of the house, with links to the trail and artists
* detail of the artist, with link to the house
* 404 section
* home page section
* footer